parameters:
Thug: Whoops, look who's here, the weakling monster who lost
twice to the same opponent! We talked about something here a
while ago, didn't we? What was it again?

Thug: Gehihi, you said you'd never lose, right? And you were
even okay with making a bet... what was it that we bet on
again?

Memimi had made a certain bet with them before the
rematch... Of course, just like the match, Memimi lost...
The problem was the content of that bet.

Memimi: (If I lose the rematch, I have to drink their urine
as a human urinal... No, that's got to be a joke, right...?
I need to find a way to talk my way out of this and get
away...)

Thug: Ah, trying to pretend you forgot and run away, huh?
Well, drinking piss is definitely too much, even if it was a
bet.

Thug: After all, someone who keeps losing to the same
opponent and has developed a habit of losing can't keep
their promises. Even Lord Shark has completely fallen from
grace... joining the ranks of the bottom-dwelling scum!

Memimi: H... da... who would do such a thing... I'm not
trying to deceive anyone!! I came here fully intending to
drink! I'll gulp down your piss without hesitation!! I may
have lost the bet, but I'm not so fallen that I'd run from
the consequences!!

Thug: Is that so, is that so? Then shall we head to the
public restroom!

Thug: Uhehe, I've been holding it in just for this... I'm
gonna make you drink plenty!

Memimi: (Aaah, I did it again, responding impulsively...
I've dug myself into a hole... I should have just groveled
and begged for forgiveness... I don't want this... why did
it come to this... I don't want to drink it...!)

Thug: Female monsters are pretty rare in the city, but a
beautiful female monster? There's only a handful of those.
Most of them hide their faces anyway...

Memimi: I never expected my true identity to be exposed so
thoroughly... Being celebrated as a beauty by everyone
around me has made life incredibly difficult...

Thug: Your face and name got revealed, and you even showed
yourself masturbating naked; it's a miracle you can live a
normal life at all!! You realize everyone's looking at you
with lewd eyes, don't pretend you don't know!

Memimi: Gyaah, shut up!! It's not like I did it because I
wanted to!! At least try to look without getting caught, you
perverts!!!

Memimi: (This is unbearably difficult to endure...! Everyone
recalls my shameful behavior and looks at me with those
strange eyes... Ugh... The scars from the battle for a
rematch are just too deep...)
